<div class="title">3-Day Coma</div>
<div class="substance">DXM & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=9%2F16loccster&Exact=1">9/16loccster</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; 9/16loccster. "3-Day Coma: An Experience with DXM & Alcohol (exp45903)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 16, 2008. erowid.org/exp/45903</div>

